            "text": "<p>“When I discovered the curly girl method, I thought I had cracked the code to perfectly defined curls. Then one day my curls stopped curling. They became weak, limp, and shine-free. I did some research and realized my water might be playing a role. I saw a big difference after just one wash. It turned out I had a lot of buildup on my hair. Thank you Qure for helping bring my curls back.”</p>",
