            "text": "<p>“My skin has cleared up so much thanks to Qure! I use the LED mask and water filter daily and it’s cleared up my acne, and my complexion so much smoother and less red! My skin feels soft and hydrated. I can actually walk out of the house without makeup now. THANK YOU QURE!!!”</p>",
