        "slider_U7gJwX": {
          "type": "slider",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Skin and hair are glowing",
            "text": "<p>“I’ve been using this filter for a few weeks now and my hair feels SO much healthier. It feels much more smooth, less frizzy, and looks glossier overall. I have also noticed less shedding. And my skin looks more hydrated and glowy - bonus!!”</p>",
